response.overview: A man sees a tree he has never seen before. During his week, he sees this same tree everywhere he goes. While falling asleep driving, he encounters the tree face-to-face. He realizes the tree was him in a past life, and he accepts the tree not as an enemy but a friend. The man dies while crashing into the tree, but his grave sprouts a new sapling.
response.tagline: Stand tall and never forget your roots.
response.title: Forest
